.DT
adjust_alignment
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
adjust_alignment

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
adjust_alignment -  This method adjusts the current alignment of the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int adjust_alignment(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the amount to change the alignment by
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the new alignment
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adjusts the current alignment of the living
object.  This is called when an object dies and handles the
mangling of the change value based on the current alignment and
the alignment of the thing dieing.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_al(), adjust_al(), set_al(), align_string()

.EP

